{"3443660": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Love Comp", "steam_appid": 3443660, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/777e985d9c17e0db3c815f73e5558750.avif?t=1755275780\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras_big/777e985d9c17e0db3c815f73e5558750.avif?t=1755275780 width=800 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一場意外讓主角誠也流落街頭。絕望之際，遠房叔叔寄來邀請，他得以前往寧靜小島展開新生活。然而叔叔卻神秘失蹤，迎接他的是久違的表妹花奈，一位開朗活潑的少女。兩人展開同居生活，也逐漸捲入島上奇妙日常與命運交織的牽絆……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>漩渦般的雙眼、破碎的生命、再度燃起的希望。牽引誠也的，是命運，還是？</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/869f7786e38d3572dc7b13ee56ac4345.avif?t=1755275780\" width=616 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/622812531285b0f79ce33872fa9eb600.poster.avif?t=1755275780\" width=616 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/622812531285b0f79ce33872fa9eb600.webm?t=1755275780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/622812531285b0f79ce33872fa9eb600.mp4?t=1755275780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/b85f4d5abf353f83c51632dc652d1e24.poster.avif?t=1755275780\" width=616 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/b85f4d5abf353f83c51632dc652d1e24.webm?t=1755275780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/b85f4d5abf353f83c51632dc652d1e24.mp4?t=1755275780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/ca0f1a45c2875e1490b184674996e9c3.poster.avif?t=1755275780\" width=616 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/ca0f1a45c2875e1490b184674996e9c3.webm?t=1755275780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/ca0f1a45c2875e1490b184674996e9c3.mp4?t=1755275780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/6c6ed0512aca383715a863d8e46fe2cb.avif?t=1755275780\" width=616 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索系統</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由探索整座島嶼，收集物品、挖掘秘密，甚至可能發現羞羞又有趣的事件。無人注視時，你會發現什麼驚喜？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>對話系統</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >興趣？感情？性？與女孩們暢談生活話題，挖掘她們最真實的一面。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>戀愛模擬要素</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >調情、建立羈絆、共同成長。提升好感、愛意與慾望，打開她們的心門。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>迷你游戲系統</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與對手展開「音樂對決」，讓花奈提升技能，見證成長！練習、排練、用心挑戰每場節奏對戰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想換個口味？透過扭蛋系統召喚朋友與熟人，展開荒唐卻刺激的「RPG戰鬥」！用派砸臉打倒難纏敵人！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>H系統</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >強化「技巧」，解鎖嶄新互動，學會連續觸碰，與花奈共創最極致的親密體驗。畢竟她可是主角，當然要給她最棒的！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>豐富劇情</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >歡笑、淚水、曖昧與心動。每位女主都擁有專屬的情感故事，浪漫又不失火花，令人難以忘懷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/654724513966c9ec56c7d55d6cff3ea0.avif?t=1755275780\" width=616 height=146 /></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/777e985d9c17e0db3c815f73e5558750.avif?t=1755275780\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras_big/777e985d9c17e0db3c815f73e5558750.avif?t=1755275780 width=800 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一場意外讓主角誠也流落街頭。絕望之際，遠房叔叔寄來邀請，他得以前往寧靜小島展開新生活。然而叔叔卻神秘失蹤，迎接他的是久違的表妹花奈，一位開朗活潑的少女。兩人展開同居生活，也逐漸捲入島上奇妙日常與命運交織的牽絆……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>漩渦般的雙眼、破碎的生命、再度燃起的希望。牽引誠也的，是命運，還是？</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/869f7786e38d3572dc7b13ee56ac4345.avif?t=1755275780\" width=616 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/622812531285b0f79ce33872fa9eb600.poster.avif?t=1755275780\" width=616 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443660/extras/622812531285b0f79ce33872fa9eb600.webm?t=1755275780\" type=\"vi